<table width=75%>
<tr><td bgcolor="#0000AF">
<strong><font color=white>
<center>Gearheart The Rogue Quest</center>
</font></strong>
</td></tr>
</table><BR>
<div align="left">
1) Talk to the warrior guild master in Ak'Anon to get the quest.<BR>
<BR>
2) Travel to Lesser Faydark and find Gearheart.  He is either in the small Gnome settlement just inside the zone border close to Steamfont Mountains or he is in the Faerie Ring.   <BR>
<BR>
3) Kill Gearheart and he will drop Gearheart's gearbox.<BR>
<BR>
4) Take this box back to the guild master for a faction adjustment, some exp, random piece of raw-hide armor, and some coin.</div>
<BR>
